Concepts

Phlagrantfile
    This file describes how Phlagrant will set up your Virtual Machine. Phlagrantfiles all extend the base
    PhlagrantfileBase Model, in the PhlagrantRequired Module complete. This base model provides groups of
    default settings for your Virtual Machines. You

Networking
    Basic Usage
    Forwarded Ports
    Private Network
    Public Network

Synced Folders

